    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This weapon is a kama and a weighted end, connected by a length of chain. You can wield it as a kama (1d6 slashing), a chain with a weighted end (1d6 bludgeoning), or as a double weapon, in which case you treat it as though wielding two light weapons. Weapon specific feats do not apply unless they specifically affect the kusari-gama, and weapon-specific feats you take for the kusari-gama do not affect attacks with a kama or a chain. The Kusari-Gama Style feat offers additional benefits.</p>",
